data.description: Calling all investors, this triplex has a great income with stable rents. 2 established tenants in place and currently one vacant unit. Tenants pay for PG&E, property owner pays all other utilities. Each unit is a 1 bed, 1 bath with stackable laundry in each. The bathrooms have tile shower stall, ductless heating and cooling units for comfort, dishwashers and included with purchase is a fully fenced adjoining lot for extra yard space or potential for storage or additional units. Close to public transit, shopping and Austin Park.
